# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible. The image builds the
# demo from source via Maven, so prebuilt output and tooling caches are excluded.
**/target
**/node_modules
.git
.github
.idea
.vscode
*.iml
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Root-level planning/scratch Markdown (already git-ignored) — not needed to build.
/*.md
